 1.3 Log login attempts
    What was changed
    Updated AuthController login endpoint to capture client IP via HttpServletRequest.
    Updated AuthService login method signature to accept ipAddress.
    Added LoginAttemptService usage in AuthService:
    logs success=false when authentication fails (then rethrows the same auth exception)
    logs success=true after successful authentication

    Every /auth/login request now records an attempt with:

    email
    success (true/false)
    ipAddress
    timestamp

